sections.text:
A municipality may cooperate with:

A. any other municipality;

B. any county or any flood control authority;

C. the state of New Mexico; or

D. any agency of the United States, in carrying out the objectives of Sections 3-41-1 through 3-41-5 NMSA 1978.

History:1953 Comp., § 14-42-5, enacted by Laws 1965, ch. 300.
